Audiveris won't build if you're using JDK version 9. The dependency Lombok throws a NullPointerException appears to not support JDK9 yet: https://github.com/rzwitserloot/lombok/issues/985

First snapshot about schemas and documentations about .omr format.
- A Gradle 'schemas' sub-project handles the automatic building of
annotated XSD schemas and HTML documentations.
- JAXB is used to generate raw schemas from Java code
- jaxb2-maven-plugin is used to inject JavaDoc as schemas annotations
- xs3p + xsltproc are used to build HTML from annotated XSD files
